{"tid":1320611,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"中撚晒伏big big channel","createTime":"2019-07-15T12:22:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T09:57:50.000Z","uid":268327,"like":14,"dislike":687,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"fff26d62b47d1471089459f7c6e006c14eccbe61","tid":1320611,"uid":268327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T12:22:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />事源係同屋企人一齊睇左無線東張西望講個大陸桃點必汁出來點正點正之後就即刻上網訂左兩盒陽山水蜜桃試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌佢老未，逼人一買買兩盒都算...七百幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />先講下送貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n夜晚差唔多9點打比我，同我約時間話第二朝10點送貨。<br />\n隔左唔夠一個鐘，差唔多10點又打來！話啲桃送到黎我屋企門口！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後果啲咩必汁標水乜都唔見...都算！<br />\n<br />\n重 點 係 ： 完全唔撚甜！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最後仲要有個係爛既.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V24RffD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV24RffD.png&h=f9654d19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸野真係大陸野，狗也不屌垃圾桃賣到五十幾蚊粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我咁都中伏我都覺得我好豬兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eace71d5bc2269ac156198eb8a583309f258f1ac","tid":1320611,"uid":58351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T12:23:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1462789790aabc765b73198961761aed592ea472","tid":1320611,"uid":129169,"like":124,"dislike":0,"score":124,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T12:23:17.000Z","msg":"on9 仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc24f37a00c931ca1043c6450ceb354002766e2","tid":1320611,"uid":153,"like":123,"dislike":0,"score":123,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T12:23:43.000Z","msg":"Royal級都唔識學人食"},{"pid":"cb8d141eb01ed389948f078b73095a30b02959be","tid":1320611,"uid":268327,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1462789790aabc765b73198961761aed592ea472","tid":1320611,"uid":129169,"like":124,"dislike":0,"score":124,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T12:23:17.000Z","msg":"on9 仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T12:23:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8389fa1f7d8e5bc5e3ec108e7bd83c57836c07ee","tid":1320611,"uid":268327,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T12:24:31.000Z","msg":"吃一個上一課<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088b04e074f9a8997c59d8a54630583065e267c6","tid":1320611,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T12:24: